---
description: Final implementation and review checklist for meaningful landing page changes
alwaysApply: false
globs:
  - "src/**/*"
  - "public/**/*"
---

definition-of-done:
- Requirements mapped to changed files.
- Canonical facts checked against the knowledge base.
- Browser tested on mobile and desktop.
- Keyboard navigation and focus tested.
- No new console errors or failed network requests.
- Typecheck, lint, tests, and build executed when available.
- Images optimized and dimensions reserved.
- Core conversion links verified.
- Analytics events verified once per action.
- SEO metadata and social preview checked.
- Known limitations documented.
- No invented claim, testimonial, logo, faculty member, scarcity, or result.
